B.a2h=new A.aq("Roulin Post \u2014 Quick User Guide\n\nOfficial In-App Reference Manual\n\nWelcome to Roulin Post, a high-level professional workspace designed to give you complete command over the information streams you consume, the networks you construct, and the collaborative spaces you manage.\n\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\n1. Core View Modes\n\n\u2022 Universal Feed\nYour global broadcasting dashboard. It aggregates general public updates, commercial announcements, news, and unfiltered media posts from users worldwide.\n\n\u2022 Custom Curation Feed (Room Mode)\nA filtered viewing landscape. Activating a specific Room dynamically restructures your window to completely suppress general noise, displaying only the updates from accounts selected inside that Room.\n\n\u2022 Chat Mode\nA dedicated workspace that hides all algorithmic public timelines to let you focus entirely on direct messages, professional deals, and secure text/media communication histories.\n\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\n2. The Custom Rooms Framework\n\n\u2022 Creating a Room\nNavigate to the profile console of any market entity or user handle, select Add in My Room, and deploy them to an existing room or instantly configure a new one.\n\n\u2022 Setting a Default Page\nOpen the Rooms Dashboard Hub via your bottom menu bar to assign a specific Room as your starting workspace. The app can bypass the public timeline to load your high-priority workspace automatically upon user login.\n\n\u2022 Inviting Collaborators\nShare your custom tracking parameters by selecting Invite to Room from a colleague's profile card. They can review and accept the request directly in their notification panel.\n\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\n3. Communication & Media Optimization\n\n\u2022 Direct Messages\nInitiate secure chat threads directly from a user's profile card or by performing a long-press gesture on their handle directly inside the public timeline.\n\n\u2022 Hardware Media Compression\nWhen you upload video files to a Room or public timeline, a native processing engine automatically optimizes and shrinks the file sizes on device hardware. This saves cellular data, ensures rapid distribution, and avoids upload latency.\n\n\u2022 Media Asset Vaults\nVisit any user profile to expand their dedicated Photo & Video Gallery. This automatically organizes their legacy attachments into crisp, easy-to-browse media grids.\n\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\n4. Data Reliability & Caching\n\n\u2022 Offline Continuity\nAn advanced two-tier caching framework retains active data feeds right on your device. If you lose internet connectivity, the application allows you to read cached conversations, view profiles, and browse your recent feed timelines smoothly.\n\n\u2022 Smart Streaming\nHeavily utilized assets, like video clips, are cached on local storage the first time you view them, preventing repetitive downloads and cutting background bandwidth costs.\n\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n\n5. Application Metadata & Support\n\nTo access system details, tap the app logo to return to the public feed or perform a long-press gesture on the top logo element to open this information panel.\n\nRoulin Post Ver 1.0 (2026)\nCreated by Devgloyd.com\n\nFor technical inquiries or more information:\nking@devgloyd.com",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
